    <item>
      <title>Pokémon Crossing: Bear Update!</title>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/501930</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">c7510341ed7f70495e822552b23faaddc6b0f49e</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 12:04:44 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/661d175a2ac8d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65fa0564898bd.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65fa066846f83.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65fa05854ba33.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65fa05716bf04.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65fa05ad92ad8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65fa05bdb1280.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65fa05d22bca7.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65fa05f380dc9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65fa05fe8a492.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65fa0607d7e89.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65fa061a70006.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65fa0621d4a62.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65fa064016334.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65fa0648f110f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65fa06579edb4.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65fa065a507fe.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65fa06612be05.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65fa0674cdd98.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65fa067b987d8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/65fa06925734f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/661d17346de34.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/661d173f05be2.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/661d175166f0a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/661d17555abe1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/661d1768a0d60.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/661d176f68fda.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/661d177d6372d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Bear Update!&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Change&lt;/em&gt;: Added Teddiursa, Ursaring, Ursaluna and Cubchoo!&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;Heya!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is a mod I have made myself in the past few days- 12 new villagers based on different Pokémon are joining Animal Crossing!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;h2 class="SelectedElement"&gt;The First batch, from the original upload!&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pachirisu&lt;/b&gt;, known as &lt;b&gt;Pachy&lt;/b&gt;, a &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Peppy &lt;/span&gt;villager replacing &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Tasha&lt;/span&gt;! She also has a custom birthday, the 8th of February, based on the Japanese release of the episode where Dawn catches her Pachirisu. She is the only one with a custom birthday.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Spinda&lt;/b&gt;, a &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Lazy &lt;/span&gt;villager replacing &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Claude&lt;/span&gt;!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Skitty&lt;/b&gt;, known as &lt;b&gt;Eneco &lt;/b&gt;(Skitty's Japanese name), a &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Normal &lt;/span&gt;villager replacing &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Lolly&lt;/span&gt;!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pansear&lt;/b&gt;, known as &lt;b&gt;Seary&lt;/b&gt;, a &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Jock &lt;/span&gt;villager replacing &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Monty&lt;/span&gt;!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Female &lt;b&gt;Oinkologne&lt;/b&gt;, known as &lt;b&gt;Oinka&lt;/b&gt;, a &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Snooty &lt;/span&gt;villager replacing &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Pancetti&lt;/span&gt;!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pancham&lt;/b&gt;, a &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Smug &lt;/span&gt;villager replacing &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Vladimir&lt;/span&gt;!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Miltank&lt;/b&gt;, known as &lt;b&gt;Milky&lt;/b&gt;, a &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Big Sister&lt;/span&gt; villager replacing &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Naomi&lt;/span&gt;!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Lycanroc&lt;/b&gt;, a &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Cranky &lt;/span&gt;villager, replacing &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Wolfgang&lt;/span&gt;!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;br&gt;The second batch, from the Bear Update!&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Teddiursa&lt;/b&gt;, known as &lt;b&gt;Teddy&lt;/b&gt;, a &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Lazy &lt;/span&gt;villager, replacing &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Chester&lt;/span&gt;!&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Ursaring&lt;/b&gt;, known as &lt;b&gt;Ursa&lt;/b&gt;, a &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Cranky &lt;/span&gt;villager, replacing &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Curt&lt;/span&gt;!&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Ursaluna&lt;/b&gt;, known as &lt;b&gt;Luna&lt;/b&gt;, a&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt; Big Sister&lt;/span&gt; villager, replacing &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Ursala&lt;/span&gt;!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Cubchoo&lt;/b&gt;, known as &lt;b&gt;Choo&lt;/b&gt;, a &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Lazy &lt;/span&gt;villager, replacing &lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Pudge&lt;/span&gt;!&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;There were no preferences in the Pokémon picked, I just picked whoever I felt like would be easy to make, and would fit a specific personality. This mod is there just for fun, so I'd say none of the textures are perfect, but I think it's part of the charm honestly.&lt;br&gt;Only the &lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;textures, personalities for the ones who needed it and names in English&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt; have been changed, to change their clothes and catchphrase, you'd have to do it in the save editor, which is very simple. The photos they give you have not been edited either, and I don't think I'll ever edit them. Sorry!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;I'm also simply not done with this mod, as I simply wanted to make a villager of each personality and all of different species before releasing it, but I'm certainly going to add more Pokémon and update this mod in the next days. There's no gen 1 Pokémon for now, but they'll come eventually! Stay tuned!&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/pokemon_crossing_bear_update.rar" type="application/vnd.rar"/>
      <category>Villagers</category>
      <category>Skins</category>
    </item>
