cannot say which b.c. i dont know ????. But it doesnt matter because you cannot really see the low resolution of the villagers in the gameplay.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;br&gt;Some other things:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;There are some items that aren´t in 4K right now cause they look bad in 4K or the charm was taken away. And also; you need to use a version of acnl that is below version 1.4. I would recommend version 1.0.</description>
